org.aksw.iguana.utils.comparator

Class LivedataComparator2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aksw.iguana.utils.comparator.LivedataComparator2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<java.io.File>

    public class LivedataComparator2
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<java.io.File>
    The Class LivedataComparator. Compares LiveData Strings ([0-9]{6}\\.(added|removed)\\.nt) with the given strategy INSERTS_FIRST Strings with added will be before Strings with removed. Rest will be orderd by the number. DELETES_FIRST Strings with removed will be before Strings with added. Rest will be orderd by the number. INSERT_DELETE First order by number than by added before removed DELETE_INSERT First order by number than by removed before added
    Author:
    Felix Conrads
